### Problem
The original FloRaSat implementation is incompatible with newer INET versions due to:
- Missing interfaces (ScalarReception)
- Changed include paths
- Deprecated analog model APIs

### Fixes Implemented

#### 1. LoRaReceiver.h
- Updated include path for SNIR handling

#### 2. LoRaReception.h
- Reimplemented as standalone class
- Removed dependency on deprecated INET classes

#### 3. LoRaAnalogModel.cc
- Simplified analog signal model
- Replaced outdated interfaces
- Added SNIR-based signal evaluation

### Outcome
These fixes enable successful integration of FloRaSat with INET 4.x and OMNeT++ 6.x.


Note:
These implementations are simplified versions for compatibility and simulation purposes.
They do not represent the full physical layer accuracy of LoRa communication.

